\title{Citizen-Science Quantum and Chaos Simulations Orchestrated by the Codette AI Suite}
\author{Jonathan Harrison\\Raiffs Bits LLC\\\texttt{jonathan.harrison@example.com}\\ORCID: 0009-0003-7005-8187}
